595
00:49:34.683 --> 00:49:36.768
Who among you
would be first?

596
00:49:38.144 --> 00:49:40.146
(all murmuring)

597
00:49:47.153 --> 00:49:49.155
(Vermithor grumbles)

598
00:49:53.451 --> 00:49:55.036
(grumbling)

599
00:50:06.673 --> 00:50:08.904
I have nothing
more to tell you.

600
00:50:08.905 --> 00:50:11.136
