- (smallfolk yelling)

629
00:53:42.139 --> 00:53:44.557
(Vermithor screeches. roars)

630
00:53:45.725 --> 00:53:46.935
(screams)

631
00:53:47.686 --> 00:53:48.853
(grunts)

632
00:53:49.854 --> 00:53:51.856
(smallfolk screaming)

633
00:53:55.610 --> 00:53:57.654
- No!
- Shh. shh. shh!

634
00:53:57.655 --> 00:53:59.698
