635
00:54:02.784 --> 00:54:04.786
(smallfolk screaming)

636
00:54:06.871 --> 00:54:08.289
(roars)

637
00:54:08.290 --> 00:54:09.708
(screaming)

638
00:54:16.715 --> 00:54:18.132
(roars)

639
00:54:18.133 --> 00:54:19.551
(panting)

640
00:54:20.385 --> 00:54:22.387
(smallfolk screaming)

641
00:54:23.430 --> 00:54:25.432
