642
00:54:26.641 --> 00:54:28.643
(Vermithor grumbles)

643
00:54:31.146 --> 00:54:32.772
(screeches)

644
00:54:37.402 --> 00:54:38.987
(roaring)

645
00:54:42.741 --> 00:54:43.908
(grunts)

646
00:54:48.163 --> 00:54:49.789
(grumbling)

647
00:54:52.917 --> 00:54:54.127
(groans)

648
00:54:55.170 --> 00:54:57.964
(smallfolk panicking)

649
00:54:57.965 --> 00:55:00.759
Here!
Here I am!

650
00:55:00.760 --> 00:55:02.427
(roaring)

651
00:55:13.521 --> 00:55:15.064
I'm ready.

652
00:55:15.065 --> 00:55:16.608
(roaring)

653
00:55:30.538 --> 00:55:33.394
