670
00:58:07.153 --> 00:58:09.989
- (roars)
- (heavy footsteps)

671
00:58:14.327 --> 00:58:15.954
(grumbles)

672
00:58:19.666 --> 00:58:21.876
(Ulf grunting)

673
00:58:29.968 --> 00:58:31.636
(grumbling)

674
00:58:48.403 --> 00:58:50.405
