taken to wing.

688
00:59:39.662 --> 00:59:42.082
Your brother expects
to join the fight soon.

689
00:59:42.083 --> 00:59:44.167
guard (shouts):
Dragon!

690
00:59:44.542 --> 00:59:46.168
Ironrod:
And when he does.

691
00:59:46.169 --> 00:59:49.025
