will be unstoppable.

692
00:59:49.026 --> 00:59:51.883
guard (shouts):
Dragon! Inside! Now!

693
00:59:51.884 --> 00:59:55.095
(indistinct shouting outside)

694
00:59:59.766 --> 01:00:02.769
